headline: Synchrony (SYF) Q4 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: Synchrony (SYF) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 0.53% and 0.77%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
